<div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-3">
    <div class="card text-center border border-2 border-dark rounded-5">
        <div class="card-body cardColor rounded-5">
            <h2>User Settings</h2>
            <h3>My Role: {{user.role.name}}</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container border border-3 border-dark rounded-5 text-center my-4 cardColor">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-stretch my-3 gap-4 px-4">
        <div
            class="border border-2 border-dark w-50 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-5 settingsContainer">
            <div class="card text-center text-white w-50 fs-5 border border-3 border-dark rounded-5">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Change is good, especially when it comes to your profile picture. Upload a fresh image to keep
                        your
                        online presence up-to-date and stylish. 🌟🖼️</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <img src={{user.profileImage.url}} alt={{user.username}} class="w-50 rounded-5">
        </div>
        <div
            class="w-50 border border-2 border-dark rounded-5 py-3 px-3 settingsContainer d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
            <form action="/users/settings/picture" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <h3>Change Profile Picture</h3>
                <div class="my-4">
                    <input class="form-control form-control-lg border border-2 border-dark" type="file" id="formFile"
                        name="image">
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-danger btn-lg px-5 border border-2 border-dark" type="submit">
                    Change <i class="fa-solid fa-image"></i>
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container border border-3 border-dark rounded-5 text-center my-4 cardColor">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-stretch my-3 gap-4 px-4">
        <div
            class="border border-2 border-dark w-50 px-3 py-3 rounded-5 settingsContainer d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center gap-3">
            <div class="card text-center text-white border border-3 border-dark rounded-5 w-50">
                <div class="card-body fs-5">
                    <p>🆕 Ready for a fresh start? Update your username and show the world your renewed identity! 🚀
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card text-center text-white border border-3 border-dark rounded-5 w-50">
                <div class="card-body fs-5">
                    <p>🔄 Changing your username is like turning a new page. What will your next chapter be called? 📖
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
            class="w-50 border border-2 border-dark rounded-5 py-3 px-3 settingsContainer d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
            <form action="/users/settings/username" method="POST">
                <h3>Change Username</h3>
                <div class="form-floating my-4">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control border border-2" id="floatingInput" name="username"
                        placeholder="username" value="{{user.username}}">
                    <label for="floatingInput">Username</label>
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-danger btn-lg px-5 border border-2 border-dark" type="submit">
                    Change <i class="fa-regular fa-user"></i>
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>